headline: Amphenol (APH) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of electrical connector manufacturer Amphenol (NYSE:APH) jumped 5.7% in the afternoon session after analysts at Goldman Sachs and BofA raised their price targets, citing the company's growing role as a key supplier for the artificial intelligence (AI) industry.
